When you believe all these beliefs to be true and you don't get worry, anger or doubt it means you got it.
If you get any of the emotions that means you believe them for the wrong reasons or you simply not believe them at all.
It means your belief lives in a different world. Not in the world of enlightenment.

0. Each belief is true and false sometimes.

1. EVERYTHING is true in some worlds and false in some other universes.

2. I have no control over anything

3. Nothing is forever

4. There is no me

5. I need to know why

66. I know exactly what each belief really is. I know when and why it came and where it came from. I know where it goes and I know what it does. I know exactly how to deal with it.
